TASK:
There are specific access levels for users defined by the xFusionCorp Industries system admin team. 
Rather than providing access levels to every individual user, the team has decided to create groups with required access levels and add users to that groups as needed.

See the following requirements:
a. Create a group named nautilus_admin_users in all App servers in Stratos Datacenter.
b. Add the user mohammed to nautilus_admin_users in all App servers.

COMMANDS:
ssh tony@stapp01
sudo su -
groupadd nautilus_admin_users
id mohammed
useradd -G nautilus_admin_users mohammed
id mohammed
exit

ssh steve@stapp02
sudo su -
groupadd nautilus_admin_users
id mohammed
useradd -G nautilus_admin_users mohammed
id mohammed
exit

ssh banner@stapp03
sudo su -
groupadd nautilus_admin_users
id mohammed
useradd -G nautilus_admin_users mohammed
id mohammed
